name: Sinister Halloween Oculus Go
summary: Experience a Halloween Haunted Experience in OculusGO. Halloween night and you decide to take a shortcut to the big party. Are you brave enough to pass through a Haunted Forrest?  Play one level, explore the haunted forest and shoot werewolves and defeat a haunted Boss.  We planned to make a demo for the Oculus GO store page, but now Oculus doesn't support new Go games for the store.
